title: File:VB - Kyndil Sunset Kappingin February 2012.JPG
author: EileenSanda
description: Handball match in the Faroe Islands in the women's best division, which is called Sunset Kappingin or Sunsetdeildin. The match was between VB Vágur (red and blue) and Kyndil from Tórshavn (green and black). VB won this match 29-26.
